  creatureName: Changeling
  image: {fileID: -9120784594126226781, guid: 59b2e3cf4b5a1b94e97a69bab59b2772, type: 3}
  description: "The Changeling is a cunning mimic that takes the place of a stolen
    child, wearing a fragile disguise of innocence. Beneath the false surface, it
    is a unsettling creature that likes to confuse and upset families. \nThe disturbing
    feeling might not be noticable at first, but the uneasiness slowly grows. "
